{"tid":1761844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[運動未完，馬上起行！] 先行者罷工計劃，招募敢炒隊！","createTime":"2019-11-29T07:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T13:36:17.000Z","uid":89974,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e026a8fff841034c49f920e2c8f3ad94f00911ed","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:25:42.000Z","msg":"我地係先行者，一班唔怕被解僱，願意為社會出多一份力既人。<br />\n<br />\n極權步步進逼，由解放軍出動，二噁英毒氣滿佈，到以武力攻擊校園，以屠殺為目標。雖然近期我們先後贏得區選，並獲人權法案簽署，然而我們距離五大訴求，以及清算警隊仍然有一段距離。同時，中共將會重新審視對香港的形勢，更劇烈的打壓將會重臨。今日再唔反抗，我們將會迎來最悲慘既結局---新彊般既種族清洗。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我正式呼籲各位無負擔/敢於犧牲參與<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「罷工宣言」</span></span>行動，透過遞信俾老細/同事，甚至係工司群組內發放文宣，去正式宣佈無限期罷工，為其他仲有負擔既人做一個榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做，除咗可以打破囚徒困境(因為已知有&quot;1&quot;個人肯罷)，亦可以令香港經濟呢個緊密既齒輪鬆脫。<br />\n<br />\n一個人既罷工其實無大家想像如此無用：<br />\n香港既高物價高薪金令人手長期緊張，一個人既罷工會令整間公司運作減緩，公司運作放緩就會令其生意既合作夥伴受到影響；一環扣一環下，社會就會漸漸癱瘓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQ4tFJQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQ4tFJQ.png&h=279ac7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: small;\">只要有第一個先行者，就能打破人等我我等人既罷工困境</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">因此，請務以令全公司的人都知道你會罷工先有效。</span><br />\n<br />\n行動：<br />\n1.發送文宣(whatsapp/email/打印)俾老細同事，宣佈你要罷工<br />\n2.嘗試與同事傾一傾而家處境有幾嚴峻，盡量說服佢地罷工<br />\n3.係社交媒體同朋友圈子內不停發佈，推post，務求令更多人知道呢件事<br />\n4.加入我地一齊宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dM4ENGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdM4ENGF.jpg&h=5f2c6f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGZ101F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGZ101F.jpg&h=e2e01ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDKmgz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDKmgz1.jpg&h=7be4141b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WP9dR8n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWP9dR8n.jpg&h=9a168ded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">理念請仔細睇Q &amp; A ︰</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ1︰罷工算唔算和理非？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA1 ︰罷工係暴力之外，亦即係和理非既最終手段！政府管治既係社會而非死物，所以只要將社會癱瘓，民不聊生，政府將會逼於無奈妥協！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ2︰可唔可以「被罷工」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA2 ︰因為「被罷工」而返唔到工，果D叫做比老闆扣大假或者出No Pay Leave，最多叫多日假，一點壓力都比唔到政府！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ3︰點樣達成「真。罷工」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA3︰除咗等待工會同基金搞掂之外，如果閣下無太大負擔，完全可以學我地咁提交罷工宣言，直接同老細傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ4︰都未有工會/保障基金，點罷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA4︰首先工會同基金已經搞緊，但實在追唔上局勢惡化既進度！如果你係為咗薪金，為咗福利，咁樣大台的確係有必要，因為咁先可以確保你唔會俾資方針對；然而而家已經係生死存亡之際，大屠殺隨時來臨，各區充滿毒氣，無論你係為咗信念，健康定係安全，你都應該隨時準備罷工！二噁英並唔會理你係番工定係唔番工，你都會同樣中毒！我地已經去到種族滅絕既最後關頭，就只差臨門一腳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ5︰可唔可以一個行業或一間公司咁發動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA5︰可以！但唔一定要！如果你公司有幾個志同道合嘅義士，一齊SEND罷工宣言就更好，被炒機會大大減低，最好同一個部門，你公司無可能即刻代替你地！威力更大！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ6︰一個強大的罷工行動要咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA6︰首先要有唔怕無得撈嘅第一梯隊，然後要有會跟進嘅第二、第三梯隊，只要多D人走出宣佈罷工就會成功！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ7︰點算成功罷工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA7︰社會癱瘓，香港死城，直到政府回應五大訴求，按人權法推出真普選！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ8.全間公司都係藍喎，罷完無人跟，有咩用？<br />\nA8.對於公司內無同伴既手足黎講，罷工最大既得著就係玩殘你班藍到黑既同事！份宣言你同事都會睇到，變相係一個大型文宣。你俾人炒咗，藍絲就要繼續OT，二噁英繼續日日食，令佢地早死幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ9.罷一兩日有鬼用，等工會搞好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA9.我地先行者係要求無限期罷工而非罷一兩日就完。我地亦預咗唔會特別多人，但只要有一定數量既人罷工，社會就會慢慢停頓落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且黃絲人數多過藍絲，只要有第一個人肯罷工，其他黃絲又跟住響應，癱瘓部門/公司/行業其實並非無可能！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家按自己能力入群！同時我們亦更加容易聯合到相同處境既人士！<br />\n1.第一梯隊：如果你願意做罷工敢炒隊，請去呢度：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/353CbNN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F353CbNN&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=e2e513ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/353CbNN</a><br />\n2.第二梯隊：如果你公司有人做敢炒隊就會跟住罷工，請入呢度︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37bMbXd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37bMbXd&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=2a8810fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37bMbXd</a><br />\n4.如果真係有好多人罷工/要有工會先罷工請入呢度︰<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=c8db36e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n5.如果你只想得知最新消息請去公海︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2rHLbJV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rHLbJV&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=23285237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2rHLbJV</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n香港需要你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3da67d49f56371cf598fff1ec74fd06b126536a0","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tZLs0Lj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZLs0Lj.jpg&h=d67fd90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyN3y5j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhyN3y5j.jpg&h=90508de4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87a5d790aa2d7b63f66c854f4ebf43913a932032","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acPJy5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacPJy5p.jpg&h=3d63cd2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkN7giL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkN7giL.jpg&h=05f80287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUJBT5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUJBT5q.jpg&h=7e017d8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01c9b586cda1ed6d4e193c0d696eb9666444b2fd","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNxK2YX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNxK2YX.jpg&h=ff4fc125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOsnPDX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOsnPDX.jpg&h=299d55a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9pNgiY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9pNgiY.jpg&h=ed664e46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"829c48e494d6a5aeeaadbb31e0212402cd0b8ed2","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsO6wSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsO6wSX.jpg&h=31796fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzKdWjD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzKdWjD.jpg&h=e813a7d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9ad8cf5255763d86996676c1b7204199442eed7","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HrTbS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HrTbS4.jpg&h=fadbd2c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVJN0Ms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVJN0Ms.jpg&h=7d4eebfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"944b7207e79d73012a21dd45fb3c8f2d75da59ae","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"d6f4e9e8d309155118862ba90cc56ed57052c601","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7caeaa0b9c6d384f7a1df06074871e307f133a","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65837cb9284c078a7c397ecbdd1ef815fcee9f9","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4224dd30fc36aadcd66aeb448025fd32e3c5f375","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3131fc23a11dbb005766caf7b70623f41e57e6","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc5cb51fd2a249b2e0d8345067576a582728683","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da68eff6342962a130a0884bc24fe0d4ea0dbd4","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7eda2d988ef4b8f1dbe3f7faf8e99a63b95b1e7","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a311b8dcc5af2c087ae53b082201a79cbfde6da2","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44450095c96eedf47efaaad1bd67c95eed3e4a71","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760ef594d39cc01d0a912c2839c4a67886b366fb","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e1701bd977e209061422d2586c2cacc7f167ca","tid":1761844,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6381dd370dbc91c39625921703f74501bb889e9a","tid":1761844,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5b65aa71e11febe92726653cbb25530128e79c3","tid":1761844,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:38:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f46a4bb9b4cd476e124c0dce0700a4b1a1c173ee","tid":1761844,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:43:30.000Z","msg":"打工仔，反抗"},{"pid":"de2c7d3be611a8e8d1279940057dd6611e8861a0","tid":1761844,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:43:44.000Z","msg":"打工仔，反抗"},{"pid":"78785644d9a8cc5f2797c9b81c50522929f094fd","tid":1761844,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T20:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46381bf8826f95b85f9cf9626355ee9ebb41fbf","tid":1761844,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T20:33:07.000Z","msg":"工會先"}]}